{"tid":1716501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[檢討]唔知有無人察覺信息傳遞係效率上有好大問題","createTime":"2019-11-13T10:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T13:01:56.000Z","uid":142764,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"87582898aefedb1e7e76b238edc41c2136177c0b","tid":1716501,"uid":142764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:57:09.000Z","msg":"第一次開post勿屌得咁大力<br />\n簡單講<br />\n近日睇到好多ig story只不過係repost以下ig既post <br />\n@airdropeverywhere<br />\n@appledailyhk<br />\n@stand.for.hk<br />\n@thestandnews<br />\n@hkpoliticalmemes<br />\n都有一定數量，不能盡錄<br />\nrepost既人大多數都發表下自己感受 加句屌你老母咁上下既野<br />\n甚至只係repost 連意見都無<br />\n但問題就係呢度<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你去瘋傳已經瘋傳緊既資訊，你明唔明自己做緊乜?</span></span><br />\n相信有follow上面等等ig既人都會接收到有關資訊<br />\n唔係限制你唔準表達自己意見<br />\n而係你一個人出十個story我要睇幾多個重複而唔急切既post?<br />\n例子就係如果琴日中大急需物資<br />\n你係要傳呢類急切既資訊 <br />\n而唔係係個ig瘋狂屌狗又唔出黎又唔傳緊急既資訊<br />\n依家每日資訊都好多，要接收晒都要花時間，大家不如傳下日程時間表、緊急野。<br />\n另外<br />\n每個人有唔同既參與度<br />\n有人屋企mon實晒出唔到，去識日文就twitter做日文文宣<br />\nat least有參與<br />\n不割<br />\n總結:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請follow大ig page/tg channel，唔好再傳人人都知既資訊</span></span>"},{"pid":"06c56716fcfe5c92cba81f33c25d99dc70aca2a2","tid":1716501,"uid":320299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:58:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">推下，睇意見<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">（p牌好似推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ca293a2ec38e8a6ff047e64234dd79fd5d5a3d36","tid":1716501,"uid":142764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:59:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f007ff2e5a0f9d2706d88f02b0a78aea6bfb30ac","tid":1716501,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor